title: Nine West Women's One Step Ready Pull On Jegging
description: STYLE - Pull on jegging with midrise hidden elastic comfort waistband, usable back pockets, mock front details and skinny fit
VERSATILITY - Goes great with all tops from fashionable to tee shirts and all your favorite footwear for the flexability you want
LENGTH - This flattering jegging come in a 27.5" short inseam, 29.5" regular inseam and 31.5" long inseam, all with 10" leg opening
Nine West Jeans - Designed for the eternally evolving modern woman and merges her vivacious sensibility with trending jeanswear essentials
